OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776272750
OL,3,CThieves steal over 100 memorial
OL,4,Cplaques from crematorium
OL,6,FOver a hundred memorial plaques could
OL,7,Fbe melted down and sold as scrap after
OL,8,Fthey were stolen from a crematorium
OL,9,Fgarden.
OL,11,FStaff at Overdale Crematorium in
OL,12,FBolton turned up to work on Monday 13
OL,13,FApril to discover that 114 metal
OL,14,Fplaques commemorating loved ones had
OL,15,Fbeen stolen over the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
