FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776272750
OL,3,CThieves steal over 100 memorial
OL,4,Cplaques from crematorium
OL,6,FLocal councillor David Grant labelled
OL,7,Fthe incident a "disgusting crime" and
OL,8,Fencouraged anyone who had been
OL,9,Faffected to get in touch with
OL,10,Fcrematorium staff who can order a
OL,11,Freplacement plaque.
OL,13,FThe thefts are only the latest
OL,14,Fincident at the crematorium, which saw
OL,15,Fmore than 800 memorial plaques stolen
OL,16,Ffrom the same gardens in July 2024.
OL,18,FWhile the material used to make the
OL,19,Fplaques is very cheap, the thieves may
OL,20,Fbe intending to melt them down and
OL,21,Fsell them as scrap.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776272750
OL,3,CThieves steal over 100 memorial
OL,4,Cplaques from crematorium
OL,6,FBolton Council, in a statement on
OL,7,FTuesday, said it has been reported to
OL,8,Fthe police, who are investigating.
OL,10,FThe statement said: "Council officers
OL,11,Fbelieve that even though the plaques
OL,12,Fare made of gunmetal, which is very
OL,13,Flow value compared with brass and
OL,14,Fother metals, the thieves may try to
OL,15,Fsell them to scrap metal merchants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776272750
OL,3,CThieves steal over 100 memorial
OL,4,Cplaques from crematorium
OL,6,F"However, tighter rules governing
OL,7,Fscrap metal dealers make selling the
OL,8,Fplaques much more difficult, as anyone
OL,9,Fsupplying scrap to a merchant must
OL,10,Fprovide photo ID and a bank account,
OL,11,Fas payment in cash is illegal. Anyone
OL,12,Fwho finds their plaque is missing
OL,13,Fshould report the matter to Overdale
OL,14,FCrematorium office.
OL,16,FA council spokesperson added: "This is
OL,17,Fa disgusting crime and it is difficult
OL,18,Fto believe anyone could sink to the
OL,19,Flevel of stealing plaques
OL,20,Fcommemorating loved ones from a
OL,21,Fmemorial garden.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776272750
OL,3,CThieves steal over 100 memorial
OL,4,Cplaques from crematorium
OL,6,F"Some of them mean a great deal to
OL,7,Fpeople and have been visited regularly
OL,8,Ffor decades, meaning people will be
OL,9,Fheartbroken to find them missing.
OL,11,F"The council is working with the
OL,12,Fpolice to identify those responsible
OL,13,Fand anyone who believes their loved
OL,14,Fone's memorial has been stolen is
OL,15,Fencouraged to get in touch to discuss
OL,16,Fa replacement."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
